skins.shipDescription: Kaidai Type VIa submarine C I-168.
skins.selfIntroduction: I am the submarine I-168. In the war, I avenged Hiryuu by taking out Yorktown and Hammann. Besides that... well... I really tried... but wasn't able to sink any other ships...
skins.acquisition: I'm I-168, but do call me Iroha. I expect you to know how to handle an extraordinary and decorated vessel such as myself!
skins.login: You're very late! ... A submarine such as myself is extremely patient, but that doesn't mean you can keep me waiting for this long...
skins.details: You want something from me, don't you? ... Well, even if you don't...
skins.secretaryIdle2: I'm tired... I like it better in the ocean...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Hammann? If she wants to berate me then she can go ahead and try! I'll turn the tables on her!
skins.secretaryTouch: Don't touch me for no reason! ... It's a massage? O-okay... Continue...

skins.shipDescription: I look different from usual? That's obvious, isn't it... All right, all right, I was just giving you a hard time. We're at a festival, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!
skins.acquisition: I look different from usual? That's obvious, isn't it... All right, all right, I was just giving you a hard time. We're at a festival, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!
skins.details: Fried squid! Dango! Candied apples! Om nom nom... *Cough cough*! N-need water...!
skins.secretaryIdle1: I just love festivals! You have my permission to take a break today? ... It's the other way around?
skins.secretaryIdle2: G-going around town every now and then isn't so bad, I guess...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Hammann can't tie her yukata's sash on her own either... W-what's so funny?! Hardly anyone can tie that thing on their own!
